### Create menu item (expect 201)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Hamburger", "price": 8.99 }

###

### Create menu item (expect 201)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Medium Fries", "price": 3.49 }

###

### Create menu item — duplicate name (expect 409)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Hamburger", "price": 9.99 }

###

### Create menu item — invalid price (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Bad Item", "price": -1 }

###

### Get all active menu items (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems

###

### Get menu item by id (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems/1

###

### Update menu item (expect 200)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems/1
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Hamburger", "price": 9.49 }

###

### Delete (soft) menu item (expect 204)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems/1

###

### Get all — deleted item should not appear (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems

###

### Get deleted item by id — still accessible (expect 200, isActive: false)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menuitems/1
